        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
          <li>‚Ä¢ Academic coursework in database management, network security, and system administration</li>
          <li>‚Ä¢ Active participation in online learning communities and forums</li>
          <li>‚Ä¢ Planning to contribute to open-source DevOps projects to gain collaborative experience</li>
          <li>‚Ä¢ Preparing for AWS Cloud Practitioner certification to validate cloud knowledge</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

