    <p class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400 sm:leading-7 lg:leading-8 sm:text-base lg:text-lg mb-4">
      DevOps represents the perfect intersection of my interests: technology, automation, security, and problem-solving.
      I'm fascinated by how DevOps practices can transform the way teams build, deploy, and maintain software systems.
      The culture of collaboration, continuous improvement, and automation aligns perfectly with my values and career aspirations.
    </p>

    <div class="p-4 my-6 bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 rounded-lg">
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-green-800 dark:text-green-300 mb-2">üöÄ What I Can Bring to an Internship:</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-green-700 dark:text-green-400">
        <li>‚Ä¢ Strong theoretical foundation combined with hands-on learning experience</li>
        <li>‚Ä¢ Eagerness to learn and adapt to new technologies and practices</li>
        <li>‚Ä¢ Security-minded approach to infrastructure and development</li>
        <li>‚Ä¢ Fresh perspective and enthusiasm for modern DevOps practices</li>
        <li>‚Ä¢ Commitment to continuous learning and professional development</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h2 class="mt-8 mb-4 text-2xl font-bold dark:text-neutral-200">My Learning Timeline</h2>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <div class="relative pl-8 before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-2 before:w-2 before:h-2 before:bg-blue-500 before:rounded-full">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">Current Focus (2025)</h3>
        <ul class="mt-2 text-sm space-y-1 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
          <li>‚Ä¢ Completing AWS Solution Architect certification</li>
          <li>‚Ä¢ Building portfolio projects demonstrating DevOps practices</li>
          <li>‚Ä¢ Contributing to open-source projects</li>
          <li>‚Ä¢ Seeking internship opportunities</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="relative pl-8 before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-2 before:w-2 before:h-2 before:bg-green-500 before:rounded-full">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">2024 Achievements</h3>
        <ul class="mt-2 text-sm space-y-1 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
          <li>‚Ä¢ Completed 5 major TryHackMe learning paths</li>
          <li>‚Ä¢ Started university IT program</li>
          <li>‚Ä¢ Completing AWS Cloud Practitioner certification</li>
          <li>‚Ä¢ Gained hands-on experience with Linux and scripting</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="mt-8 mb-2 text-2xl font-bold dark:text-neutral-200">Let's Connect!</h2>
    <p class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400 sm:leading-7 lg:leading-8 sm:text-base lg:text-lg">
      I'm excited about connecting with industry professionals, fellow students, and anyone passionate about DevOps and cloud technologies.
      Whether you're looking for an eager intern, want to discuss the latest in DevOps, or have advice for someone starting their journey,
      I'd love to hear from you! Feel free to <a href={siteConfig.links.linkedin} target="_blank" class="text-indigo-600 underline">connect with me on LinkedIn</a>,
      check out my learning projects on <a href={siteConfig.links.github} target="_blank" class="text-indigo-600 underline">GitHub</a>,
      or send me an <a href={`mailto:${siteConfig.links.email}`} class="text-indigo-600 underline">email</a> to start a conversation.
